Package me.Salt.Command.Commands.Fun.CardsAgainstDiscord

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CaDAddPlayerCommand
    This command is used to add a player to a Cards Against Discord game.
    CaDCreateGameCommand
    This command is used to create a new Cards Against Discord game, which is tied to the user's ID.
    CaDEndGameCommand
    This command checks if the executing user has an instance of a Cards Against Discord game and - if they do - ends the game.
    CaDInfoCommand
    This command is used to retrieve information about the executing user's Cards Against Discord game -- if they have one.
    CaDRemovePlayerCommand
    This command is used to remove a player from a Cards Against Discord game.
    CaDStartGameCommand
    This command is used to start a Cards Against Discord session, owned by the command executor.
    CaDViewGamesCommand
    This command prints a list of embeds to the textchannel of the command's execution.
